Graphics.MyApplication - is the main class and contains all graphics

Game.Simulation - drives the simulation forward as long as the user wants it
if the simulation should be on or not

Game.Board - Contains all available cells
also contains the side size

Graphics.Tile - Describe a specific tile is a Rectangle


Game.Cell - Describes the cell as a living being
Needs to be known
if it will live next round or not
what color it is
which tile it is connected to

Game.Rules - has the rules to decide if a cell will be born, continue to live or die
- calculation methods to decide if it will be alive or not
